title: #192 - The Death Of H3H3 By Gokanaru
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast Ethan addresses the infamous "Death of H3h3" video by YouTuber Gokanaru. People have been demanding Ethan respond to this video for years now so- here we are. Enjoy.
